{
  "stem": "12289.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it's interesting to know that this first group, I gave those passports to, were the-- the big business people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "For instance, there was the-- the head of the Tungsram.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] And that's the big factory, working lamps and all that, electrical firm.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was a Swedish-owned.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I remember, still remember when he came to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "His name was Wohl, Hugo Wohl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he come up to me in my apartment, hiding his yellow star, like that, and said, Per, now you must help me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, what-- what can I do?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean it-- it's-- And then I came to think of, why don't I give you a pass, a Swedish passport, like that, a Swedish provisional passport, he and his family, and-- and-- also his next in command and so on and so on.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And those-- this group of people then, later on, became the-- the closest cooperators-- collaborators with Raoul Wallenberg.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you can imagine the-- the competence.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, they have been heading big firms and organizers and used to-- to solve situations in different-- different aspects like that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you already have-- have been the boss for hundreds of people working in a factory and all that and so on, you had a routine and to go on organizing and-- and how to put the right man in the right place and so on.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they became the staff, this-- the first staff of Raoul Wallenberg.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they put up all these-- of his offices.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so Raoul Wallenberg had very, very competent co-workers at the beginning.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I had already saved them before he came, so to say.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
